<a name="toc_tc28915"></a><p>&nbsp;</p><div> <table class="tc" width="90%" ><tr><th colspan="4">Test Case P237-30: ECP_Valid_AddProdus&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 80%;">[Version  : 1]</span></th></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Author:</span></td><td colspan="3">tmir3641</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Summary:</span><br /><p>Se verifica functionalitatea de adaugare a unui produs nou la nivel de service, cu nume nenul si pret &gt; 0.</p>
</td></tr><tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Preconditions:</span><br /><p>name: string, not null and not empty</p>

<p>price: double, &gt; 0</p>

<p>id: int, &gt; 0</p>
</td></tr><tr><td><span class="label">#:</span></td><td><span class="label">Step actions:</span></td><td><span class="label">Expected Results:</span></td></tr><tr><td width="5">1</td><td><p>Se introduc datele pentru un nou produs: nume = &quot;pepsi&quot;, pret = 5.0, CategorieBautura = &quot;JUICE&quot;, TipBautura = &quot;BASIC&quot;. Se creeaza produsul si se executa metoda de adaugare</p>
</td><td><p>Produsul creat este salvat fara erori in sistem.</p>
</td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Execution type:</span></td><td colspan="3">Automated</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Estimated exec. duration (min):</span></td><td colspan="3"></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Importance:</span></td><td colspan="3">Medium</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"></td></tr><tr><td > name of the autotest class:</td><td  colspan = "3" >ProductServiceTest</td></tr>
<tr><td > name of the test method:</td><td  colspan = "3" >testAddProduct_ECP</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Requirements</span><td colspan="3">tmir3641_F01:  AdaugareProdus [Version : 1]<br /></td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Keywords:</span></td><td colspan="3">&nbsp;None<br/></td></tr>
</table>
</div>
<a name="toc_tc28919"></a><p>&nbsp;</p><div> <table class="tc" width="90%" ><tr><th colspan="4">Test Case P237-31: ECP_Invalid_AddProdus&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 80%;">[Version  : 1]</span></th></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Author:</span></td><td colspan="3">tmir3641</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Summary:</span><br /><p>Se verifica functionalitatea de adaugare a unui produs nou la nivel de service, cu atributul <strong>name </strong>vid.</p>
</td></tr><tr><td><span class="label">#:</span></td><td><span class="label">Step actions:</span></td><td><span class="label">Expected Results:</span></td></tr><tr><td width="5">1</td><td><p>Se introduc datele pentru un nou produs:&nbsp;nume = &quot;&quot;, pret = 5.0, CategorieBautura = &quot;JUICE&quot;, TipBautura = &quot;BASIC&quot;. Se creeaza produsul si se executa metoda de adaugare</p>
</td><td><p>Sistemul nu adauga produsul si se arunca exceptie de tip ValidationException cu mesajul: &quot;Numele nu poate fi gol!&quot;</p>
